data.description: This gorgeous two-story 3,033 sq. ft custom Lennar NextGen home is located on the largest lot (7,100 sq. ft) in the development with all the upgrades.  The downstairs level features an open floor plan with a great room that looks over the formal  dining area and a gourmet kitchen. The gourmet kitchen features a large entertainers island, stainless steel appliances including two ovens, microwave, dishwasher, large refrigerator, upgraded beautiful kitchen cabinets, quartz countertops with a separate pantry area. Downstairs has a convenient half bathroom as well. This home offers a full NextGen ADU featuring a kitchenette, its own family room, laundry room, full bathroom and bedroom as well as its own separate entrance from the main house and separate backyard space. Great for additional rental income or multigenerational families. The upstairs level has a large loft/family room, two bedrooms, two full bathrooms, laundry room and a large primary suite with a large walk in closet.   The home features the latest in energy efficiency including solar. And no HOA.  Fully landscaped backyard perfect for entertaining. Electric, gas and water lines installed for an outdoor kitchen. Covered porch entertainment area, as well as a separate space for the fire-pit to enjoy on cool evenings.
